column5: 25 days till my fly-in to Birch Lake with KayAir....so pumped I feel like a little kid at Christmas. My wife is sick of hearing about it....I better be quiet or there could be repurcussions.....
Don't worry.. the repercussions won't happen until you get back and they will be much easier to deal with, after a week away! HH
You'll have a good week.  Be on time because Pete is punctual.  You won't need walleye helper when preparing your meals.
I know it...he told us 8:00 which means be there by 6:30 get weighed and we will have air under the wings by 7:50ish....I assume you mean we will have no problem catching walleyes?????
